title: Elastic scattering of deuterons by 9Be and 28Si

x4freetext: Elastic scattering of deuterons by 9Be and 28Si
Targets were prepared by evaporation of beryllium or
silicon from a tanatalum boat onto thin silver foils
Some of the measurements were made with targets
prepared by evaporation of both materials. Typical
targets were 15 keV thick for 1MeV deuterons.
